const content = "<div class=\"container single-page-container\">\n\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-single-page-wrap col\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-page-title-wrap nv-big-title\" >\n\t<div class=\"nv-page-title \">\n\t\t<small class=\"neve-breadcrumbs-wrapper\"></small>\t\t<h1>Cookie Policy</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n</div> \n\t<div class=\"nv-content-wrap entry-content\">\n<p>This Cookie Policy explains how WorkSmart-AI (“we”, “our”, “us”) uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit our website. It should be read together with our <a href=\"/privacy-policy/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://worksmart-ai.co.uk/privacy-policy/\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. What are Cookies?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device (computer, tablet, smartphone) when you visit a website. They allow websites to function properly, improve performance, and provide information to site owners.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We use the following categories of cookies:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>a. Essential Cookies</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Necessary for the website to function (e.g. security, page navigation, form submission).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Without these, the site cannot operate correctly.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>These do <strong>not</strong> require your consent.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>b. Analytics &amp; Performance Cookies</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Help us understand how visitors use our site (e.g. Google Analytics).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Provide insights on which pages are most popular, how long users stay, and where traffic comes from.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data is aggregated and anonymous.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>c. Functionality Cookies</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Remember choices you make (e.g. language preference, form entries).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improve user experience.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Third Party Cookies</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Some cookies may be set by third-party services we use, such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> (website analytics).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Microsoft Forms </strong>(analytics)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Social Media Platforms</strong> (e.g. LinkedIn).</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These providers may use cookies independently. We encourage you to review their privacy and cookie policies.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. How to Manage Cookies</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You have the right to decide whether to accept or reject non-essential cookies.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>On your first visit, our <strong>cookie banner</strong> will ask for your preferences.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can update or withdraw your consent at any time by adjusting your browser settings or re-opening the cookie banner.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Browser Controls:</strong><br>Most browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. You can usually:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Delete existing cookies.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Block all cookies.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allow only certain types.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Please note: Blocking essential cookies may affect the website’s functionality.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Duration of Cookies</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Session cookies</strong>: Deleted when you close your browser.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Persistent cookies</strong>: Remain on your device for a set period or until you delete them.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We review our cookies regularly to ensure they remain necessary and proportionate.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on our website, with the “effective date” shown at the top.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Contact Us</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions about this policy or how we use cookies, please contact:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>📩 <a href=\"/contact-us/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://worksmart-ai.co.uk/contact-us/\">Contact Us</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n</div>";
